WEBVTT

00:03.462 --> 00:07.512
NARRATOR: For centuries,
mankind has been the dominant species.

00:07.674 --> 00:12.805
We've domesticated animals,
locked them up, killed them for sport.

00:12.971 --> 00:19.024
But what if all across the globe,
the animals decided, "No more?"

00:19.186 --> 00:22.565
What if they finally
decided to Hght back?

