- L.A. Telegraph.
- You're the animal coroner?

01:18.453 --> 01:19.796
Veterinary pathologist.

01:19.955 --> 01:23.801
The beef those lions were fed
came from cows that fed on grain

01:23.959 --> 01:26.587
