with each other.

01:33.677 --> 01:36.772
JACKSON: Abe.
- If you go, I go with you.

01:36.930 --> 01:40.104
Besides, I think Japanese
women are very sexy.

01:40.267 --> 01:42.235
I'm sure they're gonna
find you sexy too,

01:42.394 --> 01:43.771
in a beaten-up kind of way.

01:44.313 --> 01:46.281
- Chloe Tousignant?
- Oui.

01:46.440 --> 01:48.534
You may be uniquely
suited to help us.

01:48.692 --> 01:52.663
