03:00.097 --> 03:02.600
but I needed to show you tangible
evidence of what I suspect

03:02.766 --> 03:04.860
- you are beginning to realize.
- And what is that?

03:05.018 --> 03:08.693
That something very strange is
occurring in the animal kingdom.

03:08.855 --> 03:10.983
And I'd like your help in
getting to the bottom of it.

03:11.149 --> 03:14.198
Why me? I'm not a field agent.

03:14.361 --> 03:17.240
