sorry, I'm not your girl.

03:19.574 --> 03:22.623
Miss Tousignant,
I've thoroughly vetted you.

03:22.786 --> 03:25.539
You're one of the top
intelligence analysts at the DGSE,

03:25.706 --> 03:27.504
you speak five languages,

03:27.666 --> 03:30.636
you understand virtually
every culture on Earth.

03:30.794 --> 03:33.047
