23:01.839 --> 23:04.888
In Alaska, my 40th birthday.

23:06.427 --> 23:08.896
Reiden Global. Heh.

23:09.346 --> 23:11.519
We have been fighting
that fight for some time,

23:11.682 --> 23:14.105
- haven't we, Ms. Campbell?
- Yes, we have, senator,

23:14.268 --> 23:15.941
but Dr. Morgan has found

23:16.103 --> 23:19.403
the smoking gun we've
been waiting for.

23:20.608 --> 23:22.906
Yeah. Right. Uh...

23:23.068 --> 23:26.663
It's possible that a new mutation
is allowing lions in Los Angeles

23:26.822 --> 23:30.247
to communicate with each
other over long distances.

23:30.784 --> 23:33.162
Functioning as some
sort of superorganism.

23:33.329 --> 23:36.503
Although the evidence of this is
observational, not quantitative.

23:36.665 --> 23:41.011
What Dr. Morgan didn't mention is
that the mutation in the lions,

23:41.170 --> 23:44.094
and some disturbing behavior
we witnessed in cats,

23:44.256 --> 23:47.851
was preceded by exposure
to Reiden pesticides.

23:48.010 --> 23:51.139
We can finally show
that Reiden is radically

23:51.305 --> 23:54.980
- altering animal genetic code.
