into Reiden Global.

24:09.406 --> 24:11.625
For every motion we
file, they file ten.

24:11.784 --> 24:14.082
For every lawyer we
have, they have a dozen.

24:14.244 --> 24:18.249
Reiden is just too powerful.
They're everywhere.

24:18.415 --> 24:19.507
Well, senator, this

24:19.667 --> 24:22.887
I know this has been important to
you for some time, Ms. Campbell,

24:23.045 --> 24:24.763
but it is over.

24:25.339 --> 24:28.263
- Well, we should go, Jamie.
- Please.

24:28.425 --> 24:32.020
Knowing when there's no longer
any sense in a fight, Jamie,

24:32.179 --> 24:35.058
