28:47.768 --> 28:49.190
Why?

28:49.353 --> 28:53.699
Look, I really appreciate
everything that you've done so far,

28:53.857 --> 28:55.609
but there's nothing
for me there.

28:57.069 --> 28:58.821
I'm gonna go call my uncle.

28:58.987 --> 29:01.160
See if I can crash with
him till my next setback.

29:07.955 --> 29:09.832
MAN: Mitchell Morgan.

29:11.583 --> 29:13.005
Uh...

29:13.877 --> 29:15.254
Do I know you?

29:25.138 --> 29:29.518
As you can see,
the matter is rather urgent.

29:31.019 --> 29:33.021
So you claim,

29:33.563 --> 29:37.659
Mystery Man in a Very Nice Suit.

29:37.818 --> 29:40.367
I'm in town, actually.
Um... Heh.

29:40.529 --> 29:43.533
Yeah. Yeah, for work.

29:43.699 --> 29:46.794
Yep. With the paper. Uh...

29:47.202 --> 29:49.079
I, um...

29:49.496 --> 29:51.464
