animal in the world.

34:15.971 --> 34:18.520
No. I mean, of course not, right?
That's ridiculous.

34:18.681 --> 34:21.025
Only a crazy person would

34:21.184 --> 34:22.902
think that.

34:25.063 --> 34:26.485
The radiation on the island

34:26.648 --> 34:30.118
seemed to accelerate the
horses' violent behavior.

34:30.277 --> 34:34.748
Equine Number 12 at one point
attacked my assistant...

34:34.906 --> 34:36.908
[l\/IINAKO YELLING]

