35:24.706 --> 35:26.049
Heh.

35:27.667 --> 35:29.294
Jackson?

35:30.086 --> 35:31.804
What is it?

35:36.676 --> 35:38.644
I remember this day.

35:38.803 --> 35:41.101
We were in Western Mass.

35:41.264 --> 35:44.234
