36:20.595 --> 36:22.973
[HELICOPTER WHIRRING]

36:23.807 --> 36:25.559
Come on. Hey.

36:32.524 --> 36:35.198
- Hey! Hey!
- Hey! Hey!

36:35.360 --> 36:36.987
- Hey!
- Hey!

36:51.459 --> 36:54.713
- Let's go, Mr. Oz, Mr. Kenyatta!
